              <strong>Key Insight:</strong> Moving from CLB 7 to CLB 9 adds <strong>+20 language points</strong> to your total score. This single improvement is one of the highest ROI changes you can make — equivalent to gaining over 3 additional years of work experience, yet achievable in just 2-3 months of focused preparation. Because the cap is 40 pts and CLB 8 and CLB 9 both hit 40, the practical target is <strong>CLB 9 in all four skills</strong>.
            </p>
